Grammar

    0 $accept: Program $end

    1 Program: Decls

    2 Decls: Decls Decl
    3      | ε

    4 Decl: FuncDecl
    5     | VarDecl
    6     | TypeDecl
    7     | TypedefDecl

    8 TypedefDecl: TYPEDEF VarType IDENTIFIER SEMICOLON
    9            | TYPEDEF STRUCT IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE IDENTIFIER SEMICOLON
   10            | TYPEDEF UNION IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE IDENTIFIER SEMICOLON

   11 FuncDecl: STATIC VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON
   12         | STATIC VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES FuncBody
   13         | VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON
   14         | VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES FuncBody

   15 FuncBody: LBRACE Stmts RBRACE

   16 VarDecl: STATIC VarType VarList SEMICOLON
   17        | VarType VarList SEMICOLON

   18 TypeDecl: _VarType SEMICOLON

   19 VarType: _VarType
   20        | CONST _VarType

   21 _VarType: BuiltinType
   22         | STRUCT IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   23         | STRUCT IDENTIFIER
   24         | UNION IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   25         | UNION IDENTIFIER
   26         | ENUM IDENTIFIER LBRACE EnumList RBRACE
   27         | ENUM IDENTIFIER
   28         | _VarType ASTERISK
   29         | IDENTIFIER

   30 VarList: VarList COMMA VarInit
   31        | VarInit
   32        | ε

   33 VarInit: IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList
   34        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN Expr
   35        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN LBRACE InitList RBRACE
   36        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN LBRACE RBRACE

   37 InitList: InitList COMMA InitItem
   38         | InitItem

   39 InitItem: Expr
   40         | LBRACE InitList RBRACE

   41 ArrayBoundList: ArrayBoundList ArrayBound
   42               | ArrayBound
   43               | ε

   44 ArrayBound: LBRACKET INTEGER RBRACKET
   45           | LBRACKET RBRACKET

   46 ParamList: ParamList COMMA Param
   47          | ParamList COMMA ELLIPSES
   48          | Param
   49          | ELLIPSES
   50          | ε

   51 Param: VarType IDENTIFIER
   52      | VarType

   53 BuiltinType: CHAR
   54            | SHORT
   55            | INT
   56            | LONG
   57            | UNSIGNED
   58            | UNSIGNED CHAR
   59            | UNSIGNED SHORT
   60            | UNSIGNED INT
   61            | UNSIGNED LONG
   62            | FLOAT
   63            | DOUBLE
   64            | BOOL
   65            | VOID

   66 FieldDecls: FieldDecls FieldDecl
   67           | ε

   68 FieldDecl: VarType MemberList SEMICOLON
   69          | SEMICOLON

   70 MemberList: MemberList COMMA IDENTIFIER
   71           | IDENTIFIER
   72           | ε

   73 EnumList: EnumList COMMA Enum
   74         | Enum
   75         | ε

   76 Enum: IDENTIFIER
   77     | IDENTIFIER ASSIGN INTEGER

   78 Stmts: Stmts Stmt
   79      | ε

   80 Stmt: Expr SEMICOLON
   81     | IfStmt
   82     | SwitchStmt
   83     | ForStmt
   84     | DoStmt
   85     | WhileStmt
   86     | ContinueStmt
   87     | BreakStmt
   88     | ReturnStmt
   89     | Block
   90     | TypeDecl
   91     | VarDecl
   92     | SEMICOLON

   93 IfStmt: IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt ELSE Stmt
   94       | IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   95 SwitchStmt: SWITCH LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES LBRACE CaseStmtList RBRACE

   96 CaseStmtList: CaseStmtList CaseStmt
   97             | ε

   98 CaseStmt: CASE Expr COLON Stmts
   99         | DEFAULT COLON Stmts

  100 ForStmt: FOR LPARENTHESES Expr SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
  101        | FOR LPARENTHESES SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
  102        | FOR LPARENTHESES VarDecl Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

  103 DoStmt: DO Stmt WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON

  104 WhileStmt: WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

  105 ContinueStmt: CONTINUE SEMICOLON

  106 BreakStmt: BREAK SEMICOLON

  107 ReturnStmt: RETURN SEMICOLON
  108           | RETURN Expr SEMICOLON

  109 Block: LBRACE Stmts RBRACE

  110 Expr: IDENTIFIER
  111     | Constant
  112     | LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES
  113     | Expr COMMA Expr
